               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> When she laid ill she had not necessaries, and wished me to pawn her things; I did, and gave her the money and tickets; two days before she died, she called her husband to her and gave him the duplicates; the shoes are mine.</p>
